%% === AcmeCorp Diagram Style Standard ===
classDef service fill:#DCFCE7,stroke:#16A34A,stroke-width:1.5px,color:#052E16;
classDef infra fill:#FEF3C7,stroke:#F59E0B,stroke-width:1.5px,color:#3B1F00;
classDef signal fill:#F3E8FF,stroke:#7C3AED,stroke-width:1.5px,color:#2E1065;

Service[Service Instance]:::service
LB[Load Balancer / Kubernetes]:::infra

Liveness[Liveness Probe - process alive]:::signal
Readiness[Readiness Probe - can accept traffic]:::signal

Service --> Liveness --> LB
Service --> Readiness --> LB
